Created 1.4.2003 from the Segdemoor unparished area. See also 
    Table 2, note (e).

Created 1.4.1974 by renaming the parish of Burnham on Sea. See 
    also Table 2, notes (b) and (e).

Created 1.4.1985 out of the parishes of Middlezoy, Othery and 
    Stoke St. Gregory. See also Table 2, note (e).

Created 1.4.1981 out of the parishes of Chilton Polden, Edington 
    and Catcott. See also Table 2, note (e).

Abolished 1.4.1981 and added to the parish of Spaxton. See 
    also Table 2, note (a).

Unparished area which until 1.4.1974 formed the parish of Bridgwater. 
    Abolished 1.4.2003 to become the parish of Bridgwater. See also Table 2, note (a).
